root.message: The STAT_CONC_DEF field for indicator 5-3-1, translated into en
root.data: Percentage of women aged 20-24 who were married or cohabiting for the first time before the age of 15, before the age of 18 is the percentage of women aged 20-24 who were married or cohabiting for the first time before the age of 15, before the age of 18 compared to the total number of women aged 20-24.
